    "description": "Welcome to <strong>Grapple League</strong>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/533af10fb88b12bbc5ea28cb01ab70db.poster.avif?t=1716960064\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/533af10fb88b12bbc5ea28cb01ab70db.webm?t=1716960064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/533af10fb88b12bbc5ea28cb01ab70db.mp4?t=1716960064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You'll soon embark upon a high-flying swinging adventure through several different worlds and levels to prove your skill against others in the League. Will you be able to conquer the various levels, reach the mountaintop and go beyond? Prove yourself as a master grappler!<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><strong>Five different worlds!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/e7fe54b807228ad9d335e421db6fd806.avif?t=1716960064\" width=600 height=84 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Ocean World!</strong> Every grappler's first world. Colorful tarp covered objects create intense obstacle courses!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The Canyon!</strong> The windy canyon makes for winding tight passageways and wide areas for free swinging!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The Mountain!</strong> Exceptional difficulty renders most grapplers unable to complete the daunting task of traveling vast distances and ascending to the peak. Prove yourself!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Space!</strong> Gravity is no longer down! This may get tricky quick!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The City!</strong> A foggy grey cyberpunk city where the fastest and only way through is by swinging across flying cars!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/b24ba3ffae13ef1bc30539be47a5273d.poster.avif?t=1716960064\" width=100 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/b24ba3ffae13ef1bc30539be47a5273d.webm?t=1716960064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/b24ba3ffae13ef1bc30539be47a5273d.mp4?t=1716960064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Swing in <i>Style</i></strong> Gain Style by swinging and grappling quickly! Manage to get up to S-Style and you'll find boost plentiful!<br><br><strong>Build Boost by building Style!</strong> Boost charges dynamically based on your speed and style while you swing!<br><br><strong>Unlockable Boost Types!</strong><br>The initial boost is incredibly handy, but some say they have found other boost types with significant advantages!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Base Boost.</strong> Jet yourself in the direction your facing! A grappler's staple.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Jump.</strong> A direct leap upwards. Exceptionally useful in some situations!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Glide.</strong> More useful than it seems. Dampen momentum in all directions except the one you're facing!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Bounce.</strong> Difficult to master, but improbably handy. An isosphere that reflects anyone who impacts it perfectly. Also grappleable. Nice.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>More?</strong> Rumor has it there was another, hidden and lost to space!</li></ul><br><strong>Endless Mode</strong><br>Master all the courses available? Get some distance in this endless run where instead of time, distance is your foe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/23d9b6376b66e7daadd8ace07b587ada.poster.avif?t=1716960064\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/23d9b6376b66e7daadd8ace07b587ada.webm?t=1716960064\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363790/extras/23d9b6376b66e7daadd8ace07b587ada.mp4?t=1716960064\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>The Ultimate Test</strong><br>With Steam Leaderboards enabled test yourself against your friends and the best of the best. Think you're the greatest? Prove it!<br><br><i>Swing and fling yourself into the finish!</i>",
